sources.title: Damaged Goods | Full Drama Movie | Danny Vinson | Hannah Alline
sources.description:
Damaged Goods - With an ex-boyfriend who is taking her money, a boss threatening to fire her, and a landlord who won't fix her apartment, Amanda's life is falling apart. So, when her estranged father comes back into her life, diagnosed with a fatal liver disease and she is the only match, she is faced with a crossroads. Will she continue to run from her pain, will she save her father who abused her, or will she walk away and let him die? Forced to decide, Amanda realizes she can no longer run from the past.
2021.  Stars: Hannah Alline, Danny Vinson, Abi Van Andel
